An allometric approach was developed to express N uptake and distribution in crops not unlike the approach described above for plant mass changes. Lemaire and Salette (1984a, b) and Greenwood et al. (1990) showed that shoot N uptake (Nupt, kg ha−1) was related to Wsh when Wsh was greater than 1 t ha−1:7Nupt=a×Wshb\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
